As a result of recent deregulation in states such as Pennsylvania and

California, many new companies are entering the retail energy market.  Today,

consumers in several states are able to choose their energy provider in much

the same way they choose their long-distance phone company.  A survey has

been commissioned by the research group to better understand which factors

are most important to consumers considering switching energy providers.


The survey consists of 28 question, and can be found on the following website:


http://www.energy-survey.addr.com/survey.htm


If you, your spouse, or someone else in your family has time to take this

survey, we would appreciate your input.


Feel free to forward this email to others.  Thanks for your time and

consideration.
